			<h2 class="Heading2">Instructions</h2>
	
    <section>

		<ol id="intelliTxt" class="steps">
						<li class="section">
								<ul>
								<li class="step ">
															<span class="stepNumber">1</span>
														<div class="stepMeat">
																<div itemprop="step">
									<p>In a bowl, make a mixture of milk, sugar, and flavoring. For one serving, use: one glass of milk (whole milk makes a richer ice cream), 2 tablespoons of sugar, 2 tablespoons of flavoring (chocolate powder, flavored syrup, etc.)</p>								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
																<li class="step ">
															<span class="stepNumber">2</span>
														<div class="stepMeat">
																<div itemprop="step">
									<p>Stir the mixture until mixed well and pour into a small plastic bag and seal or tie the bag.</p>								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
