									'<p class="copy">{!= ads[i].line2 !} {!= ads[i].line3 !}</p>',
									'<a rel="nofollow" href="{!= ads[i].url !}" target="_blank" title="go to {!= clean(ads[i].visible_url) !}" class="baseurl url">',
										'{!= ads[i].visible_url !}',
									'</a>',
								'</li>',
							'{! } !}',
							'</ul>',
						'</div>'].join('')
				}
			});
		</script>
	</div>
						</li>
																<li class="step ">
															<span class="stepNumber">3</span>
														<div class="stepMeat">
																<div itemprop="step">
									<p>Find a large plastic bag without holes. Blow air into it to make sure it doesn't have holes. Any large plastic bag that you get at the grocery store will do.</p>								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
																<li class="step ">
															<span class="stepNumber">4</span>
														<div class="stepMeat">
																<div itemprop="step">
									<p>Fill the bag half-full with ice. Add about 2-3 tablespoons of salt.</p>								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
																<li class="step ">
															<span class="stepNumber">5</span>
														<div class="stepMeat">
																<div itemprop="step">
									<p>Put the smaller bag into the bigger bag that contains the ice. Tie or seal the bigger bag.</p>								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
																<li class="step ">
															<span class="stepNumber">6</span>
														<div class="stepMeat">
																<div itemprop="step">
									<p>Shake the bag for 3 minutes.</p>								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
																<li class="step ">
															<span class="stepNumber">7</span>
														<div class="stepMeat">
																<div itemprop="step">
									<p>Open the bags, and inside the small bag, you will find your homemade ice cream which is ready to serve in a bowl and eat. Enjoy your delicious dessert!</p>								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
																<li class="step ">
															<span class="stepNumber">8</span>
														<div class="stepMeat">
																<div itemprop="step">
									<p>Next time, experiment with mixing different flavors, or making multiple flavors of small bags within the one big bag.</p>								</div>
							</div>
						</li>
															</ul>
						</li>
					</ol>
	</section>
	<!-- google_ad_section_end() -->

	
	</section>
